Name: NBF 01 Import Vendors and Style Classes

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: sync swatch products
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause:
VendorId is null 
and StyleClassId is  null
and StyleParentId is null

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: sync variant products
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause: VendorId is not null and StyleParentId is not null

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: sync base product
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause: VendorId is not null and StyleClassId is not null

ShippingCharges,
